FROM title t, movie_companies mc, cast_info ci
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year  <  2002 AND mc.company_id  <  100523 AND ci.person_id  <  2214275 AND ci.role_id  <  10
